Mojox-CPAN-Uploader version 0.0.1

Mojo way to upload files to CPAN

INSTALLATION

To install this module, run the following commands:

	perl Makefile.PL
	make
	make test
	make install

Alternatively, to install with Module::Build, you can use the following commands:

	perl Build.PL
	./Build
	./Build test
	./Build install


SYNOPSIS

        mojo-cpanup --user=user --pass=pass file.tar.gz
        mojo-cpanup --user=user file.tar.gz
        mojo-cpanup file.tar.gz
        mojo-cpanup file.tar.gz subdir


DEPENDENCIES

Mojolicious.


